Unless you have entered into a specific license agreement granting you additional rights, your use of this software is limited by the terms of the actual license agreement you have entered into with Monotype. Barlow Semi Condensed Thin Regular (BarlowSemiCondensed-Thin.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Barlow Semi Condensed' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Thin' = NID 1 'Barlow Semi Condensed Thin'.

NID 6 is 'BarlowSemiCondensed-ThinItalic', Everything looks good.

Barlow Semi Condensed ExLight Regular (BarlowSemiCondensed-ExtraLight.ttf)

MS NID 16/17

Barlow Semi Condensed ExLight Italic (BarlowSemiCondensed-ExtraLightItalic.ttf)

name

Mac NID 6

Mac NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'BarlowSemiCondensed-ExtraLightItalic', Everything looks good.

Pass

name

MS NID 16/17

(NID 16 + 'Space' + NID 17) 'Barlow Semi Condensed ExtraLight Italic' ≠ 'Barlow Semi Condensed ExLight Italic' (NID 1 + 'Space' + NID 2).

NID 16 'Barlow Semi Condensed' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Light' = NID 1 'Barlow Semi Condensed Light'.

Barlow Semi Condensed Light Italic (BarlowSemiCondensed-LightItalic.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Barlow Semi Condensed' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Light Italic' = NID 1 'Barlow Semi Condensed Light' + 'Space' + NID 2 'Italic'.

Pass

Barlow Semi Condensed Regular (BarlowSemiCondensed-Regular.ttf)

name

Mac NID 6

Mac NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'BarlowSemiCondensed-Regular', Everything looks good.

Barlow Semi Condensed Regular (BarlowSemiCondensed-Regular.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'BarlowSemiCondensed-Regular', Everything looks good.

Barlow Semi Condensed Italic (BarlowSemiCondensed-Italic.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'BarlowSemiCondensed-Italic', Everything looks good.

Barlow Semi Condensed Medium Regular (BarlowSemiCondensed-Medium.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Barlow Semi Condensed' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Medium' = NID 1 'Barlow Semi Condensed Medium'.

Barlow Semi Condensed Medium Italic (BarlowSemiCondensed-MediumItalic.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Barlow Semi Condensed' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Medium Italic' = NID 1 'Barlow Semi Condensed Medium' + 'Space' + NID 2 'Italic'.

Barlow Semi Condensed SemiBold Regular (BarlowSemiCondensed-SemiBold.ttf)

name

Mac NID 6

Mac NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'BarlowSemiCondensed-SemiBold', Everything looks good.

Barlow Semi Condensed SemiBold Regular (BarlowSemiCondensed-SemiBold.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'BarlowSemiCondensed-SemiBold', Everything looks good.

Pass

Barlow Semi Condensed SemiBold Regular (BarlowSemiCondensed-SemiBold.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Barlow Semi Condensed' + 'Space' + NID 17 'SemiBold' = NID 1 'Barlow Semi Condensed SemiBold'.

Pass

Barlow Semi Condensed SemiBold Italic (BarlowSemiCondensed-SemiBoldItalic.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Barlow Semi Condensed' + 'Space' + NID 17 'SemiBold Italic' = NID 1 'Barlow Semi Condensed SemiBold' + 'Space' + NID 2 'Italic'.

Pass

Mac NID 6

Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '

NID 6 is 'BarlowSemiCondensed-BoldItalic', Everything looks good.

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'BarlowSemiCondensed-BoldItalic', Everything looks good.

Barlow Semi Condensed ExtraBold Regular (BarlowSemiCondensed-ExtraBold.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Barlow Semi Condensed' + 'Space' + NID 17 'ExtraBold' = NID 1 'Barlow Semi Condensed ExtraBold'.

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Barlow Semi Condensed' + 'Space' + NID 17 'ExtraBold Italic' = NID 1 'Barlow Semi Condensed ExtraBold' + 'Space' + NID 2 'Italic'.

MS NID 6

NID 6 is 'BarlowSemiCondensed-Black', Everything looks good.

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Barlow Semi Condensed' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Black' = NID 1 'Barlow Semi Condensed Black'.

Barlow Semi Condensed Black Italic (BarlowSemiCondensed-BlackItalic.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Barlow Semi Condensed' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Black Italic' = NID 1 'Barlow Semi Condensed Black' + 'Space' + NID 2 'Italic'.

Pass
